{"tid":879483,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"不要同兔仔洗澡! 好危險!! 🐰🌟","createTime":"2018-10-28T03:49:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T18:20:24.000Z","uid":197098,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"679858666670750dad324f8eb634a0a02fc2c5bb","tid":879483,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T03:49:44.000Z","msg":"兔子很愛乾淨，會自動自己清理洗澡。同兔仔洗澡是很危險的，會令牠精神創傷，嚇怕到呆和僵硬，經常這樣會心臟病發死。但是，有一個例外：就是如果牠們屁股被糞便粘住(poopy butthole), 可以給牠們屁股洗澡🛁(butt bath)， 但不要用手直接拉牠們的糞便，因為會連皮拉出來。要用水浸到牠們的肛門和腳然後就可以慢慢清理。兔仔是被捕獵的動物，在大自然內是每個捕獵者的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，但牠們勝於速度, 跑得快。牠們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚的。<br />\n<br />\n以下video 關於洗澡危險 和怎樣給牠們屁股洗澡:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6UcoZHBlQ80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6UcoZHBlQ80&d=llKkPcsYvsbGlS0wDODprJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=9dfb3cec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6UcoZHBlQ80</a> <br />\n<br />\n如果主人試過幫兔子洗澡，可能見過兔子用後腳站起來，左右手上下方向擦。這時候兔子其實不是同你玩水，這個姿態是代表不高興，想主人不要理會牠。以下video可看到主人給兔子洗澡時，兔子在3:26被嚇暈：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6zkyjfOq36g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6zkyjfOq36g&d=llKkPcsYvsbGlS0wDODprJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=90a955b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6zkyjfOq36g</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>資訊來源: <a href=\"https://rabbit.org/the-dangers-of-giving-a-rabbit-a-bath/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org%2Fthe-dangers-of-giving-a-rabbit-a-bath%2F&d=llKkPcsYvsbGlS0wDODprJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=ee5e92a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rabbit.org/the-dangers-of-giving-a-rabbit-a-bath/</a></strong>"},{"pid":"917fdb4de1e46a80cf835991cd16099be376315c","tid":879483,"uid":141871,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T03:54:04.000Z","msg":"係真嫁<br />\n我以前養過隻鰣仔就係沖涼嚇死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f70c06a79ebbee77274e913af9ce39253ab7893","tid":879483,"uid":3549,"like":30,"dislike":24,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T04:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180523/8e49d498879e4aa29ded627243205a87.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20180523%2F8e49d498879e4aa29ded627243205a87.jpeg&h=153f2438&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a7bde10b1fa24ff0a6c6aff30124545072ed45b","tid":879483,"uid":153418,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T04:04:32.000Z","msg":"兔仔係咪勁難養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"942aff0985f68c25f5db90e2a399d993f573b359","tid":879483,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2a7bde10b1fa24ff0a6c6aff30124545072ed45b","tid":879483,"uid":153418,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T04:04:32.000Z","msg":"兔仔係咪勁難養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T04:12:38.000Z","msg":"試過養過兩星期有隻條頸唔知做乜鳩斷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65e261921f848d0aa1f3815ef429d8d762e48f4","tid":879483,"uid":105715,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T04:12:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H3k6x_TzoIQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DH3k6x_TzoIQ&d=llKkPcsYvsbGlS0wDODprJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=a4fbb427\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H3k6x_TzoIQ</a>"},{"pid":"ab2f4969cbf9bea8c1fe48808b1c7afd5763ef54","tid":879483,"uid":29606,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T05:12:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"efa62eda0d670015928a36174254a87ead5f21c0","tid":879483,"uid":4826,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab2f4969cbf9bea8c1fe48808b1c7afd5763ef54","ti